Package magellan.library.utils.replacers

Class FilterSwitch

  • java.lang.Object
    • magellan.library.utils.replacers.FilterSwitch
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BranchReplacer, EnvironmentDependent, ParameterReplacer, Replacer
    public class FilterSwitch
extends java.lang.Object
implements ParameterReplacer, BranchReplacer, EnvironmentDependent
    Acts as a unit filter that filters units where TRUE is returned by the replacer given as parameter (and that evaluates on units).
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
